        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "THE RESCUE PARTY",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "It was with mingled feelings of excitement and trepidation that Grace Harlowe and Jessica Bright hurried toward the office of the latter's father the following afternoon.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Now that they were fairly started on their mission of rescue, they were not quite so confident as to the result.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"She can't hurt us,\" said Grace.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Your father will do all the talking. All we need to do is to take charge of Mabel, after Miss Brant gives her up.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Let us go at once, for I must be back here at five o'clock.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"What are you going to say to that terrible woman, papa?\" shuddered Jessica as they neared the Brant home.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"I'm afraid she'll scratch your eyes out.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"You haven't any idea what a crank she is, mr Bright,\" laughed Grace. \"She fairly snarled at us the other day, when we were coming from school, because she said we were taking up the whole sidewalk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Poor little Mabel, no wonder she has a scared look in her eyes all the time.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Well, here we are,\" responded mr Bright, as he rang the bell.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"We have come for you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "It was Miss Brant herself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Well, what do you want?\" she said rudely.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"You have a young girl with you by the name of Mabel Allison, have you not?\" asked mr Bright.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Yes, I have.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "What's the matter with her?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Has she been gettin' into mischief?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "She has found friends who are willing to help her until she finishes her education, and she wishes to go to them.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Oh, she does, does she?\" sneered the woman mockingly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Well, you just take her, if you dare.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Have you legally adopted her?\" asked mr Bright quietly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"That's none of your business, either.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"That will do,\" said mr Bright sternly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"We will go, but we shall take Miss Mabel with us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000024_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000024_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "You did not even take the trouble to have yourself appointed her guardian.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000024_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000024_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "You agreed to pay her for her work, but blows and harsh words are the only payment she has ever received at your hands.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000024_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000024_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "She wishes to leave you because she can no longer endure life with you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000024_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000024_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "However, you have imposed upon her for the last time, for she shall not spend another hour under your roof.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"You touch her if you dare.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "We will wait for you. As for you,\" turning to Miss Brant, \"if you try to stop her, you will soon find yourself in a most unpleasant position.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Don't you dare leave my house with any of my property, you baggage,\" she hissed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Don't pay any attention to her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000030_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000030_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "You can send her back her ridiculous things.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000030_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000030_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "You are going to be happy now, and forget all about this cruel, terrible woman.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Come, girls,\" said mr Bright.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"We have no more time to waste.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000032_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000032_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Good afternoon.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000034_000001",
