        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Grace and Jessica exerted every effort to quiet her sobs, and after a little she looked up, and, smiling through her tears, said brokenly: \"I can't believe that it's all true-that I shall never have to go back there again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
