        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Be good children, and----\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "She was interrupted by an exultant shriek, and a second later five girls appeared as by magic and gleefully surrounded the rescue party.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Mabel, however, was equal to the occasion.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "She answered their questions without embarrassment, and seemed quietly pleased at their demonstrations.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000044_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000044_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Come on, Mabel, let's go home before they spoil you completely.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_41609_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/41609/4742_41609_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "\"Considering the fact that the Bright family did two thirds of the rescuing, I suppose we shall have to respect your claim,\" said Nora, \"but remember, Jessica, that generosity is a beautiful virtue to cultivate.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "PROTECTION OF APERTURE.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "The first and simplest mode of obtaining this is by channelling the jambs and arch head; and this is the chief practical service of aperture mouldings, which are otherwise entirely decorative.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "three.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "Respecting their proper form we need not stay long in doubt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "A deep gable is evidently the best for throwing off rain; even a low gable being better than a high arch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000008_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000008_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "We shall glance at the applications of each of these forms in order.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "In the Cumberland and border cottages the door is generally protected by two pieces of slate arranged in a gable, giving the purest possible type of the first form.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "As we enlarge the structure, however, certain modifications of form become necessary, owing to the increased boldness of the required supporting arch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "This last is the perfect type of aperture protection.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "None other can ever be invented so good.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "The porches will thus be united, and form one range of great open gulphs or caverns, ready to receive all comers, and direct the current of the crowd into the narrower entrances.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000016_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000016_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "This is the form of all the noble northern porches, without exception, best represented by that of Rheims.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "In the north we glaze the sides of such projections, and they become bow windows, the shape of roofing being then nearly immaterial and very fantastic, often a conical cap.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4742_74181_000017_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4742/74181/4742_74181_000017_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4742",
        "content": "The horizontal cornice of the pediment is thus useless, and of course, therefore, retained; the protection to the head of the window being constructed on the principle of a hat with its crown sewn up.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    }
